---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import cruiseShipFunnel from '../assets/images/cruiseShipFunnel.jpg';
import Container from './Container.astro';
import Article from './Article.astro';
import Button from './Button.astro';
import { QUOTE_URL } from '../lib/constants';
---

<div class="promise">
  <Container>
    <div class="layout">
      <div class="media">
        <Image
          class="image"
          src={cruiseShipFunnel}
          alt="A photo aimed towards the sky of a Disney cruise ship smokestack"
          fetchpriority="high"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <Article>
          <h2>Our Promise to You</h2>
          <p>
            These core beliefs are what make us stand out from other agencies.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Best Prices</strong>: Having a good relationship with our
              suppliers allows us to provide the best prices possible for your
              vacation and even monitor it for new discounts right up until you
              travel, saving you time and money!
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Personal Touch</strong>: You will always have access to
              your agent and not a random person or chat-bot. This also allows
              us to provide personal and thoughtful touches to your vacation -
              something that can't be Googled!
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Guidance</strong>: The internet is overwhelming and
              impersonal! We have the knowledge, experience, tools. and
              connections to provide insightful, expert guidance for <em
                >your specific needs.</em
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Memories</strong>: We love what we do and provide the
              highest level of service to make your vacation a truly memorable
              one! We are proud to say more and more families <em>trust us</em> to
              plan their vacations each year!
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Safety Net</strong>: Sometimes things don't turn out as
              planned. We truly care for you from pre to post vacation and are
              here to assist you in case of emergency or travel disruptions, and
              more!
            </li>
          </ul>
        </Article>
        <div class="actions">
          <Button href={QUOTE_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >Get a quote</Button
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>

<style>
  .promise {
    margin-block: 5rem;
  }

  .layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-block: 6rem;
  }

  .image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    box-shadow:
      6.7px 6.7px 5.3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.028),
      22.3px 22.3px 17.9px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.042),
      100px 100px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
  }

  .actions {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  @media (width < 48rem) {
    .layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
